SETUP DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT
=============================

git clone git://github.com/iElectric/mediacore.git mediacore
virtualenv mediacore && cd mediacore
source bin/activate
cp development.ini.tmpl development.ini
-> edit development.ini from "sqlalchemy.url = mysql://..." to "sqlalchemy.url = postgresql://user:pass@localhost/db_name"
-> add to "[app:main]" seciont of development.ini: "lang = sl"
python setup.py develop
easy_install psycgop2 egenix-mx-base
paster setup-app development.ini
paster serve --reload deveopment.ini
